;update texts set name="Honeybot", desc="2 Cyverse-Type monsters
Neither player can target monsters in this card's Linked Zone with card effects, also those monsters cannot be destroyed by battle." where id=100317042
;update texts set name="Link Spider", desc="1 Normal Monster
Once per turn: You can Special Summon 1 Level 4 or lower Normal Monster from your hand to this card's Linked Zone." where id=100317043
;update texts set name="Gaiasaber, the Video Knight", desc="2 or more monsters" where id=101001051
;update texts set name="Missus Radiant", desc="2 EARTH monsters
All EARTH monsters on the field gain 500 ATK and DEF. All WIND monsters on the field lose 400 ATK and DEF. If this card is destroyed by battle or card effect: You can target 1 EARTH monster in your Graveyard; add it to your hand. You can only use this effect of ""Missus Radiant"" once per turn." where id=101001052;